title: MRD5165 Eagle Kit Targets Autonomous Aerial Robotics with Qualcomm Technology
description: The MRD5165 Eagle Kit, powered by the Qualcomm QRB5165 SoC, is tailored for intelligent, low-energy IoT-enabled autonomous systems. It features an integrated AI engine and advanced computer vision, presented in a modular design that separates the flight control unit from video processing components.
